<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Meeting Reminder</title>
  </head>
  <body
    style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;"
  >
    <div style="background: linear-gradient(to right, #4CAF50, #45a049); padding: 20px; text-align: center;">
      <h1 style="color: white; margin: 0;">Upcoming Meeting Reminder</h1>
    </div>
    <div
      style="background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px; border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px; box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);"
    >
      <p>Hello <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>
      <p>This is a friendly reminder about your upcoming mentoring session:</p>

      <div
        style="background-color: white; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #4CAF50;"
      >
        <h2 style="color: #4CAF50; margin-top: 0;">Meeting Details</h2>
        <p><strong>Date:</strong> {{date}}</p>
        <p><strong>Time:</strong> {{startTime}} - {{endTime}}</p>
        <p><strong>Duration:</strong> {{duration}} minutes</p>
        <p><strong>Location:</strong>
          <a href="{{location}}" style="color: #4CAF50; text-decoration: none;">{{location}}</a></p>
        {{#if otherParty}}
          <p><strong>{{roleLabel}}:</strong> {{otherParty}}</p>
        {{/if}}
      </div>

      <div
        style="background-color: #fff3cd; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;"
      >
        <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>‚è∞ Your meeting is scheduled in {{timeUntil}}.</strong></p>
      </div>

      <div style="margin: 30px 0; text-align: center;">
        <a
          href="{{location}}"
          style="background-color: #4CAF50; color: white; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block;"
        >Join Meeting</a>
      </div>

      <p>Please make sure you're prepared and on time. If you need to reschedule or have any questions, please contact
        us as soon as possible.</p>

      <p>Best regards,<br />The Mentoria Team</p>
    </div>
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; color: #888; font-size: 0.8em;">
      <p>This is an automated reminder from Mentoria</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>